data.title: Only Two Can Play - Film Hub Wales
data.meta_site_name: Film Hub Wales | Canolfan Ffilm Cymru
data.text:
This film is covered by our Made In Wales strategy. If you are a member of Film Hub Wales you may be eligible to submit a proposal for support. Read our Made In Wales strategy.

Film Hub Wales aims to bring more films, to more people, in more places. We are one of eight Film Hubs around the UK formed in 2013 as part of the ground-breaking initiative BFI Film Audience Network (FAN).

We are using cookies to give you the best experience on our website.
